text:
EFL FOXES ON THE RAMPAGE Leicester 3 Liverpool 1 – five things we learnt: Jamie Vardy has the eye of the tiger, there were tears for Claudio Ranieri and Liverpool have given up on this season 
Vardy bagged two goals tonight as Leicester's players gave just departed Ranieri the perfect goodbye present at the King Power by JOHN HUTCHINSON
